事。<br />\n至於每拍可以做些什麼，應該做些什麼，這些已不是樂理的范疇⋯⋯建議去學鼓，因為基本beat都係模仿鼓聲。<br />\n不過如果你想製作一首完整嘅歌，中間有beat有旋律有和弦，要學既學理就多好多。用琴學係好些，但結他都沒問題（不少樂隊只有結他沒有琴）。<br />\n要留意樂理書好多都係為咗幫你考學理試，好多睇譜，標記既知識，其實都幾煩。加上佢只係俾個框架你，你始終都要就住你想玩既音樂風格，去理解如何應用。建議先去學些基本的，然後多聽，不斷聽，令那種音樂進入你既潛意識，將來編曲才會得心應手。"},{"pid":"cb89818605ceec106ac484667a1b2c840b5a9222","tid":1873082,"uid":55874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"29dd649da171964258a452ffe0ca293164bdf650","tid":1873082,"uid":41096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab21355585ea129bdd8414b966ea30ab6b0679f7","tid":1873082,"uid":320048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:26:14.000Z","msg":"巴打一級級學定一黎就五級啊，以你過來人身份有冇咩經驗分享下<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得只要樂理掂，玩音樂簡單好多，始終都係嗰8個音，可以融會貫通"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:02:43.000Z","msg":"8個音？<br />\n你真係唔識㗎喎"},{"pid":"33d89fe8b4aaa234ef3d47fc463ca0dd3eafb345","tid":1873082,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8602846a39d1bdff4a2e8c61bb3a2a3f88ea24df","tid":1873082,"uid":53196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T19:00:21.000Z","msg":"Youtube nicechord 好和弦<br />\n或者呢到教結他同琴嘅巴打都有開po講過下樂理，可以望下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"nicechord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n0樂理睇到接觸jazz"},{"pid":"efcd2d299839c2d9ae1fa14132144aebf28b6189","tid":1873082,"uid":112523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwD2LruV3To\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgwD2LruV3To&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=a05df03b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwD2LruV3To</a>"},{"pid":"323893f07b82816022ac56c99fdb9e0990979c4d","tid":1873082,"uid":112523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,