.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TvCZHc&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=603f1446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TvCZHc</a>)<br />\n<br />\n以前我同學生考極都唔可以滿分<br />\n因為作曲實俾佢扣一兩分<br />\n但前排新syllabus實施後終於有學生有<br />\n所以加油啦 有咩需要嘅tg搵我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d3cdd99834cfee7909791fab653680fb490c63","tid":1873082,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"自己睇書"},{"pid":"52dcb9712ec083b5240ab05387367b68c806cc9a","tid":1873082,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"己考五級, <br />\n想問自學到八級難唔難?<br />\n同埋有咩書/ 網上資源for自學到八級? thx..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0171ba0ebd75bd8459180e5f74b0fe8ca87a46c4","tid":1873082,"uid":235080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52dcb9712ec083b5240ab05387367b68c806cc9a","tid":1873082,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"己考五級, <br />\n想問自學到八級難唔難?<br />\n同埋有咩書/ 網上資源for自學到八級? thx..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"唔簡單 八級樂理要求harmony嘅認識<br />\n而harmony係一樣好吊鬼嘅嘢<br />\n佢冇strict answer 但又有啲rules<br />\n要明白背後嘅理念唔簡單<br />\n而且考試係要求你去潛移默化咁用<br />\ne.g. complete piano extract<br />\n<br />\n你可以試吓買本guidelines on harmony<br />\n除咗本textbook每級有本workbook<br />\n睇吓基本four-part writing嘅規矩<br />\n有關doubling同parallel/hidden 5ths/8ves<br />\nAB Guide Book 2 我自己覺得冇咁好<br />\n因為佢少啲example 較難理解harmony"},{"pid":"dc043144d8291198e9d897a931f5517ffb1660ab","tid":1873082,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d42655f01d0f53b2c78e8ea6b41b7c1703c2fabd","tid":1873082,"uid":53196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d89fe8b4aaa234ef3d47fc463ca0dd3eafb345","tid":1873082,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"