msg":"DipABRSM要你考嘅樂器嘅8級"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"8級THEORY要求你對HARMONY同MELODY好有SENSE (當然呢D SENSE既背後有好多原理要你識晒)<br />\n要熟每個DEGREE CHORD既FUNCTION , INVERSION,PROGRESSION同VOICE LEADING 既規則,而且對MODULATION要夠敏感<br />\n基礎既對位法作曲: 幾條MELODIC LINES之間既HARMONY, MOTIVE USE AND DEVELOPMENT<br />\n之前講如果有玩開ORCHESTRA會好有幫助,因為會考晒咁多種樂器,要熟佢地既特式同RANGE同IN WHAT KEY(TRANSPOSING INSTRUMENT)<br />\n再比份總譜問INTERVAL,搵CHORD,搵CADENCE etc. ,問你幾條SEHR LANGSAM, NICHT ZU SCHNELL, FEIERLICH咩意思, 如果你玩得多BRUCKNER/MAHLER既SYMPHONY就成日會見到<br />\n(如果出法文題我都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n當然你要死記唔係話唔得,我考果陣都見好多細路哥拎住本天書係度背生字,但係有3條作曲(1. baroque counterpoint, 2. Classical piano , 3. instrumental melody) ,除非好有天份,如果唔係有以上既音樂底都幾難自學"},{"pid":"9d434554220d12229011066e563c4f74404cbac4","tid":1873082,"uid":249820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:03:43.000Z","msg":"8級上了幾堂操卷班<br />\n零級古典樂器就pass<br />\nPass真係睇識唔識答題技巧<br />\n高分就好睇你對古典類音樂的知識、風格、理論"},{"pid":"c462c98745bffb8834449e653212ad2210ee7635","tid":1873082,"uid":320048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c87670c38bdeee4229614745da641e936f0502d2","tid":1873082,"uid":19760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6feb2afd4d0df93f47124312e13b6c88fbfe232d","tid":1873082,"uid":320048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29dd649da171964258a452ffe0ca293164bdf650","tid":1873082,"uid":41096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:26:14.000Z","msg":"巴打一級級學定一黎就五級啊，以你過來人身份有冇咩經驗分享下<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得只要樂理掂，玩音樂簡單好多，始終都係嗰8個音，可以融會貫通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T20:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T00:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}